fields.Title: BOARDWALK ORB / smell of death
fields.Placement:
Area: Near the bench where you find Idiot Doom Spiral's jacket.
Details:

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Eyes up, detective. Something's no..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Eyes up, detective. Something's not right here."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant has already brought..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant has already brought a handkerchief to his nose.

fields.Title: Endurance: "Keep it in now. Don't overreact. Br..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Keep it in now. Don't overreact. Breathe.

fields.Title: Perception (Smell): "The smell... It's awful and familia..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The smell... It's awful and familiar.

fields.Title: Perception (Smell): "No, it's much worse than that."
fields.Dialogue Text: No, it's much worse than that.

fields.Title: You: "It's a dead corpse isn't it?"
fields.Dialogue Text: It's a dead corpse isn't it?

fields.Title: Perception (Smell): "Don't be naive."
fields.Dialogue Text: Don't be naive.

fields.Title: You: "Hold on, that *is* awful. (Cover yo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Hold on, that *is* awful. (Cover your nose.)

fields.Title: Jump to: [Perception (Smell): "You've never smelled anything this..."]
Perception (Smell): "You've never smelled anything this..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You've never smelled anything this bad before. It's pungent, but with a faintly cloying sweetness like cheap perfume on Death itself.
fields.Alternate1: Don't you recognize it? That hideous pungency, that faintly cloying sweetness? Only death smells like that.

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "The signs of decaying meat. It anno..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The signs of decaying meat. It announces itself from two dozen metres away. A warning, a *memento mori*.

fields.Title: Half Light: "Something cold wakes in the pit of..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Something cold wakes in the pit of your stomach: fear.

fields.Title: You: "What is it then?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What is it then?

fields.Title: You: ""Heads up, lieutenant. Something's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Heads up, lieutenant. Something's not right here."

fields.Title: You: ""Kim, what's that smell?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Kim, what's that smell?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant has already brought..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant has already brought a handkerchief to his nose.

fields.Title: You: "Oh no..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Oh no...

fields.Title: Perception (Smell): "Yes. A sense of dread washes over y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yes. A sense of dread washes over you as you look ahead.

fields.Title: You: "Goddamnit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Goddamnit...

fields.Title: You: "I don't want to be here."
fields.Dialogue Text: I don't want to be here.

fields.Title: Perception (Smell): "It doesn't help. You can still smel..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It doesn't help. You can still smell it.

fields.Title: Perception (Smell): "What is that awful smell?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What is that awful smell?

fields.Title: You: "What is it?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What is it?

fields.Title: You: "Isn't it just the rotting fish?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Isn't it just the rotting fish?

fields.Title: Perception (Smell): "A sense of dread washes over you as..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A sense of dread washes over you as you look ahead.

fields.Title: Logic: "It *is* death. It must be."
fields.Dialogue Text: It *is* death. It must be.
